{"tid":1716244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前嗰排中大校長段祟智話：尊重言論自由，但要有規矩","createTime":"2019-11-13T09:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:02:35.000Z","uid":64694,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"42976f1ab85a729073c7f40d921ccadc072d8b2e","tid":1716244,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:49:44.000Z","msg":"經過尋日佢自己食咗催淚彈之後，佢係咪終於知道邊個最冇規矩亂射催淚彈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4b9878376e1b507b3bc257efd4583e59cc5f3a","tid":1716244,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>中大生與校長對話 段祟智：尊重言論自由 但要有規矩</strong><br />\n<strong>2019-10-03 HKT 18:47</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aca6C0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAca6C0e.jpg&h=8aae6759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有中大學生發起在校內罷課遊行和集會，聲援在反修例示威行動中被捕的中大學生。<br />\n<br />\n學生下午到達校長辦公室的行政樓外，要求與校長段祟智對話，段祟智發言後返回行政樓引起學生不滿，有人闖入行政樓，期間玻璃門被打碎。<br />\n<br />\n段祟智表示，尊重學生的言論自由，但要有規矩，又話學校不是政治角力的場所。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484079-20191003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484079-20191003.htm&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0Qi9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=34ab3c45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484079-20191003.htm&h=8f00209b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484079-20191003.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n唔記得補返條link添"},{"pid":"cfe4c7d68b813ae10d31f3d0fca2befd1e681ae9","tid":1716244,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"狗: 中大校長違諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65936d87b2d369dc9640e669e426d5a0c85b3d79","tid":1716244,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:54:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abpOQ16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabpOQ16.png&h=1a9ab24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQHwOww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQHwOww.jpg&h=056adf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"b99abe3b354ab08d81d4cf036fb8e5d57317c2f3","tid":1716244,"uid":161125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"至少我覺得校長有心幫年輕人！其他呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09870478ae93503fa6d61950cc32fae9787ab0a0","tid":1716244,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eu1NntW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%